research_municipality_step.notes: Franklin Township, Somerset County, NJ operates under a Council-Manager, Plan D form of government, which is a type of mayor-council system. The Mayor and At-Large Council Members listed have terms expiring on December 31, 2027. Information for the Ward Council Members (Wards 1-5) from the provided sources indicates their terms expired on December 31, 2025. Updated information for the current Ward Council Members (terms commencing January 1, 2026) was not available in the search results.
